00:35:02,630 --> 00:35:05,300
Mamice. Gde
mi je mama?

335
00:35:15,510 --> 00:35:17,510
Dobro doli
kui. Uite.

336
00:35:20,110 --> 00:35:22,450
Hej, kako ste?
Kako ste?

337
00:35:43,540 --> 00:35:48,440
