za ulaz, nigde.

398
00:41:42,330 --> 00:41:45,030
Onda bolje da vam
neto i otpevam, a?

399
00:41:45,330 --> 00:41:48,730
Kad ste ve potroili
svu tu lovu.

400
00:42:20,000 --> 00:42:23,700
"Potovana gospoice Smit,
zovem se Hari Herbert Pejs,

